Instructions -> 

1) Fork the project 

2) cd client 

3) cd server 

4) Do npm install on both sides - client and server

5) On server folder -> create a file named -> .env

6) In the .env file -> MONGO_URL = 'paste the connection string for mongoDB database and while choosing native driver option'
   PORT = 3001
   JWT_SECRET='somehardstring'

7) On the terminal with server side -> nodemon index.js   or  node index.js

8) On the terminal with client side -> npm run start

9) Now register new user and login with it .
